51
00:01:57,217 --> 00:01:58,618
-That sounds nice.
-Yes.

52
00:01:58,685 --> 00:02:00,420
-We can use our imagination.
-Right.

53
00:02:00,487 --> 00:02:01,788
-We draw on this?
-Yes.

54
00:02:01,855 --> 00:02:04,424
-We draw on a postcard-sized paper?
-Yes.

55
00:02:04,491 --> 00:02:06,593
