57
00:02:09,195 --> 00:02:10,630
No, it isn't big.

58
00:02:10,697 --> 00:02:11,798
Nice.

59
00:02:12,499 --> 00:02:15,435
NEWBIE IN THE CLUB SCHEDULE
11:30 DOONGJI 1 DRAWING

60
00:02:15,502 --> 00:02:18,004
Reincarnation. Gosh.

61
00:02:18,505 --> 00:02:20,440
Would you like to be reincarnated?

62
00:02:20,507 --> 00:02:22,609
No, I'd like to enjoy
my current life more.

63
00:02:22,675 --> 00:02:24,944
IMPRESSED

