usually dreams of being reborn.

66
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:33,520
-Really?
-Things that you didn't get to do.

67
00:02:33,586 --> 00:02:36,789
-I think I want to start over.
-Yes.

68
00:02:36,856 --> 00:02:38,758
Why do you want to start over?

69
00:02:38,825 --> 00:02:41,728
I want to be better-looking.

70
00:02:41,794 --> 00:02:42,862
STIRRED

71
