75
00:02:48,034 --> 00:02:49,502
OH

76
00:02:49,569 --> 00:02:50,770
I'd like to be taller.

77
00:02:50,837 --> 00:02:51,838
-Your figure?
-Yes.

78
00:02:51,905 --> 00:02:53,506
