85
00:03:05,919 --> 00:03:07,620
-in your next life?
-That wouldn't be bad.

86
00:03:11,824 --> 00:03:12,926
I got it.

87
00:03:13,593 --> 00:03:14,727
I got it now.

88
00:03:14,794 --> 00:03:16,429
INSPIRED AFTER CHATTING
WITH THE MEMBERS

89
00:03:16,496 --> 00:03:19,032
Gosh. How do I draw a jet plane?

90
00:03:19,098 --> 00:03:20,099
A jet plane?

91
00:03:20,166 --> 00:03:22,001
You want to be reborn as a jet plane?

92
00:03:22,068 --> 00:03:24,704
What are you dreaming about
that you want to be a jet plane?

93
00:03:24,771 --> 00:03:25,772
-Big dream.
-How complex.

94
00:03:26,506 --> 00:03:27,507
Big dream.

95
00:03:27,574 --> 00:03:30,076
HE SQUEEZES HIS BIG DREAM
ONTO THE SMALL PAPER

96
00:03:30,143 --> 00:03:35,315
THE OTHER MEMBERS' DREAMS
ARE FILLING THE DRAWING PAPER TOO

97
00:03:35,381 --> 00:03:39,819
EVERYONE IS SILENTLY IMMERSED
IN THEIR OWN WORLDS

98
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:42,422
