99
00:03:42,488 --> 00:03:43,790
-I love it so much.
-Right?

100
00:03:43,856 --> 00:03:44,924
I love it.

101
00:03:45,491 --> 00:03:46,759
Nice way to unwind.

102
00:03:46,826 --> 00:03:49,095
TODAY'S CLUB IS ALL ABOUT
ENJOYING CALMLY WHILE SEATED

103
00:03:49,162 --> 00:03:50,196
Also,

104
00:03:50,263 --> 00:03:53,299
