as you chat with the members.

105
00:03:54,067 --> 00:03:55,501
This is what I expected.

106
00:03:55,568 --> 00:03:56,769
You are like Seokchon Lake.

107
00:03:56,836 --> 00:03:58,371
-Seokchon Lake?
-Oh, Seokchon Lake.

108
00:03:58,438 --> 00:04:00,873
You are like the ducks
floating on Seokchon Lake.

109
00:04:00,940 --> 00:04:04,677
