111
00:04:06,613 --> 00:04:08,881
-So the president runs this club.
-Yes.

112
00:04:08,948 --> 00:04:11,417
Who is next in…

113
00:04:11,484 --> 00:04:12,652
CAN'T MULTITASK

114
00:04:12,719 --> 00:04:14,921
I created this club with our manager.

115
00:04:14,988 --> 00:04:15,989
-The manager?
-Yes.

116
00:04:16,055 --> 00:04:17,223
