121
00:04:26,566 --> 00:04:27,634
NEWBIE'S FAVORITE INTEREST

122
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:29,335
I got a feeling!

123
00:04:29,402 --> 00:04:32,205
-I was just focused on drawing.
-Okay.

124
00:04:32,272 --> 00:04:34,574
But even when I drew a little,
he would compliment me.

125
00:04:35,308 --> 00:04:37,143
-He bombarded you with compliments.
-Yes.

126
00:04:37,210 --> 00:04:39,245
-He's Mr. Compliments.
-Mr. Compliments?

127
00:04:39,712 --> 00:04:41,180
-Yes, I am.
-You're Mr. Compliments.

128
00:04:41,748 --> 00:04:43,283
I love talking about this.

129
00:04:43,349 --> 00:04:45,518
I love talking about these topics

130
00:04:45,585 --> 00:04:47,654
-at clubs.
-It's embarrassing.

131
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:51,224
BU DOONG BU DOONG'S
HEART-MELTING LOVE STORY

132
00:04:51,291 --> 00:04:52,325
How nice.

133
