137
00:05:02,402 --> 00:05:03,836
-Like this?
-Rub hard.

138
00:05:03,903 --> 00:05:04,904
-Like this?
-Yes.

139
00:05:04,971 --> 00:05:06,105
Oh, okay.

140
00:05:06,172 --> 00:05:08,007
-So that's how you do it.
-Yes.

141
00:05:08,074 --> 00:05:10,276
-You can use it like pastel.
-I see.

142
00:05:10,343 --> 00:05:11,811
