144
00:05:14,147 --> 00:05:15,381
Let's call it that.

145
00:05:15,448 --> 00:05:16,449
EVEN NONSENSE IS EMBRACED

146
00:05:16,516 --> 00:05:18,284
Nice. Very nice.

147
