EXPOSED

154
00:05:30,463 --> 00:05:31,464
He got you.

155
00:05:31,531 --> 00:05:33,933
-You two are dating.
-How did you figure that out?

156
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,401
You spoke informally to him,

157
00:05:35,468 --> 00:05:38,104
