and then, drop leaves.

235
00:08:15,461 --> 00:08:19,398
I'd like to live
according to the flow of time.

236
00:08:19,465 --> 00:08:21,000
Put it next to the sloth.

237
00:08:21,067 --> 00:08:22,401
THE TREE-SLOTH UNIVERSE

238
00:08:22,468 --> 00:08:23,803
-It's perfect.
-Like this?

239
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:24,871
That's why--

240
00:08:24,937 --> 00:08:26,572
-Is the sloth there if you zoom in?
-Yes.

241
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:29,041
-Oh, it's here somewhere?
-Yes, if you zoom in.

242
00:08:29,108 --> 00:08:30,343
DESTINED TO MEET AGAIN?

243
00:08:30,409 --> 00:08:31,477
Your boyfriend…

244
00:08:31,544 --> 00:08:32,979
OH, MY

245
00:08:33,045 --> 00:08:34,814
When did you accept him as your boyfriend?

246
00:08:34,881 --> 00:08:36,515
-Accept him?
-Yes.

247
00:08:36,582 --> 00:08:38,050
-He said he liked me first.
-I did.

248
00:08:38,117 --> 00:08:41,320
-We went to see flowers together.
-Flowers?

249
00:08:41,387 --> 00:08:43,689
-We don't just draw here.
-Okay.

250
00:08:43,756 --> 00:08:46,259
When the weather is nice,
we go to a lake park

251
00:08:46,325 --> 00:08:48,027
and draw on a picnic mat.

252
00:08:48,094 --> 00:08:50,162
In the fall, we go hiking

253
00:08:50,229 --> 00:08:52,164
