514
00:18:10,923 --> 00:18:12,658
It felt like walking on grass.

515
00:18:13,492 --> 00:18:15,027
-Grass?
-It has been so long. Yes.

516
00:18:15,094 --> 00:18:17,062
We don't get to walk
on grass often, do we?

517
00:18:17,129 --> 00:18:18,464
We only walk on paved roads.

518
00:18:19,064 --> 00:18:21,633
We live intense lives
with our busy schedules,

519
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:23,502
but today felt like

520
00:18:23,569 --> 00:18:27,139
