523
00:18:34,746 --> 00:18:36,949
Even though you can't draw well…

524
00:18:37,015 --> 00:18:38,050
Oh, my!

525
00:18:38,117 --> 00:18:41,186
-You aren't exactly skillful,
-Okay.

526
00:18:41,253 --> 00:18:45,090
but you can share a lot
of your thoughts and stories here.

527
00:18:45,157 --> 00:18:47,226
The stories behind your drawings
are very rich.

528
00:18:47,292 --> 00:18:49,495
My real drawings are with my words.

529
00:18:49,561 --> 00:18:50,796
I draw with my words.

530
00:18:50,863 --> 00:18:52,831
