547
00:19:24,496 --> 00:19:25,797
It was relaxing.

548
00:19:25,864 --> 00:19:26,865
It really was.

549
00:19:26,932 --> 00:19:28,934
I felt like I had a good rest.

550
00:19:29,001 --> 00:19:33,038
The members keep engaging me
in conversations.

